data.description: This newer 4 bedroom construction built in 2019 with No HOA. No Mello Roos. This is only 1 of 4 homes with a balcony. Open concept kitchen/living area with Laminate flooring throughout the first and second floor, including the bedrooms. Kitchen has custom cabinets, granite counter tops and breakfast peninsula. Home is equipped with fire sprinklers. 2 car attached garage with direct access to the home. Close to shopping, restaurants and major streets for easy commute.
